    <entry>
      <title>初始化与清理</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/04/chu-shi-hua-yu-qing-li/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/04/chu-shi-hua-yu-qing-li/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h3 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h3><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;本章作为对 <strong>《On Java8》</strong> <code>第六章 初始化和清理</code>学习笔记的整理，希望对java中对象的创建和清理有进一步的理解。</p><h3 id="一、利用构造器保证初始化"><a href="#一、利用构造器保证初始化" class="headerlink" title="一、利用构造器保证初始化"></a>一、利用构造器保证初始化</h3><p><code>注意</code>:</p><ul><li>类的构造器会在用户使用对象前自动调用对象的构造器方法。</li><li>构造器的名称为什么要和类名相同？<ul><li>任何命名都可能与类中的其他元素的命名冲突</li><li>编译器必须始终知道构造器方法名称</li></ul></li><li>构造器没有返回值，不同于返回类型为<code>void</code>的方法。</li></ul><h3 id="二、方法重载"><a href="#二、方法重载" class="headerlink" title="二、方法重载"></a>二、方法重载</h3><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;重载简单可以理解为<code>相同的词不同的意思</code>。<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;如何区分重载的方法?只需要记住一条简单的规则，即:<code>每个被重载的方法必须有独一无二的参数列表</code>。为什么不可以通过<code>方法名</code>+<code>返回值类型</code>来区分重载的方法呢？举例如下：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-java"><code class="language-java">    <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">eat</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">boolean</span> <span class="token function">eat</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span> <span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span> <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token boolean">false</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;有些情况下，编译器可以很容易通过上下文来判断该调用那个方法。比如 <code>boolean x = eat();</code>,很显然编译器会调用第二个<code>eat()</code>方法。但是有时候在程序中并不在乎方法的返回值，只是让它产生一点效果，这样直接调用<code>eat()</code>，在这种情况下，编译器就无法区别该调用那个<code>eat()</code>方法，所以不可以通过方法的名称和返回值类型来区分重载方法。</p><h3 id="三、无参构造器"><a href="#三、无参构造器" class="headerlink" title="三、无参构造器"></a>三、无参构造器</h3><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;一个无参构造器就是不接受任何参数的构造器，它一般用来创建一个<code>默认的对象</code>。如果用户创建了一个类，但类中没有给出任何的构造器，那么编译器就会自动为该类生成一个<code>无参构造器</code>。但一旦用户定义了构造器，不管是有参的还是无参的，编译器都不会在为此类生成<code>无参构造器</code>。</p><h3 id="四、this关键字"><a href="#四、this关键字" class="headerlink" title="四、this关键字"></a>四、<strong>this</strong>关键字</h3><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;对于相同类型的对象 <strong>a</strong>和 <strong>b</strong>,如何调用这两个对象的<code>eat()</code>方法呢？代码如下:</p><pre class="line-numbers language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">Person</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">eat</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/*.....*/</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">PersonEat</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        Person a <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Person</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>b <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Person</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        a<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">eat</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        b<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">eat</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;如果只有一个eat()方法，那么怎么知道调用的是 <strong>a</strong>的还是 <strong>b</strong>的？其实<code>eat()</code>方法中第一个参数<code>隐式地</code>传入了一个操作对象的引用，如下：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-java"><code class="language-java">    Person<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">eat</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>a<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    Person<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">eat</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>b<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在实际的编程中不必也不能这样写，因为这是编译器帮我们完成的。<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;假设现在想在方法内部获得对当前对象的引用，但对象又是被<code>隐式地</code>传给编译器的，也就是并不显示的出现在参数列表中，这时候就可以用到一个关键字： <strong>this</strong>。<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><font size="3" color="red">注意：</font></strong> <strong><font size="3" color="red">this关键字只能在非静态方法内部使用</font></strong><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;当在一个类的方法中调用另一个方法时，可以不用使用<code>this</code>,因为编译器会帮我们自动加上，当然你也可以使用<code>this.drink()</code>(假如Person类中有drink()这个方法)，但是没必要。<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>this</strong>关键字只用在一些必须显式地使用当前对象引用的特殊场合，例如，用在 <strong>return</strong>语句中返回当前对象的引用。举例如下：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-java"><code class="language-java">pulic <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">Leaf</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">int</span> i <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    Leaf <span class="token function">increment</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        i<span class="token operator">++</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"i = "</span><span class="token operator">+</span>i<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        Leaf x <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Leaf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        x<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">increment</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">increment</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">increment</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;很显然，输出结果为<code>i=3</code>.</p><h4 id="1、在构造器中调用构造器"><a href="#1、在构造器中调用构造器" class="headerlink" title="1、在构造器中调用构造器"></a>1、<strong>在构造器中调用构造器</strong></h4><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;当在一个类中写了多个构造器时，为了不编写重复的代码，往往需要用一个构造器去调用另一个构造器。这可以通过 <strong>this</strong>关键字实现这样的调用。例如如下代码：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">Flower</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">int</span> petalCount <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    String s <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"initial value"</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token function">Flower</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> petals<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        petalCount <span class="token operator">=</span> petals<span class="token punctuation">;</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Constructor w/ int arg only, petalCount = "</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> petalCount<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token function">Flower</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String ss<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Constructor w/ string arg only, s = "</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> ss<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        s <span class="token operator">=</span> ss<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token function">Flower</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String s<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> petals<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>petals<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//- this(s); // Can't call two!</span>        <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>s <span class="token operator">=</span> s<span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// Another use of "this"</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"String &amp; int args"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token function">Flower</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"hi"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">47</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"no-arg constructor"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">printPetalCount</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//- this(11); // Not inside constructor!</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"petalCount = "</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> petalCount <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">" s = "</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> s<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        Flower x <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Flower</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        x<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">printPetalCount</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>输出结果:</code></p><pre class="line-numbers language-java"><code class="language-java">Constructor w<span class="token operator">/</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> arg only<span class="token punctuation">,</span> petalCount <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">47</span>String <span class="token operator">&amp;</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> argsno<span class="token operator">-</span>arg constructorpetalCount <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">47</span> s <span class="token operator">=</span> hi<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><font size="3" color="red">注意：从构造器<code>Flower(String s,int petals)</code>可以看出，通过this只能调用一次构造器。另外必须首先调用构造器，否则编译器会报错。在printPetalCount()方法中可以看到，编译器不允许在一个构造器之外的方法里调用构造器。</font></strong></p><h4 id="2、static的含义"><a href="#2、static的含义" class="headerlink" title="2、static的含义"></a>2、static的含义</h4><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><font size="3" color="red">static中不会存在this,不能在<code>静态方法</code>中调用<code>非静态方法</code>（反之可以）。</font></strong> 静态方法是为类创建的，不需要任何对象，这也是<code>静态方法</code>的主要<code>目的</code>。<code>静态方法</code>看起来就像全局方法一样，但是java不允许全局方法。<strong><font size="3" color="red">一个类的<code>静态方法</code>可以被其他类的静态方法和静态属性访问。<font></font></font></strong></p><h3 id="五、垃圾回收器"><a href="#五、垃圾回收器" class="headerlink" title="五、垃圾回收器"></a>五、垃圾回收器</h3>]]></content>
      
      
