        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aplayer/dist/APlayer.min.css"><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aplayer/dist/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/meting/dist/Meting.min.js"></script><p><embed src="//music.163.com/style/swf/widget.swf?sid=333750&type=2&auto=1&width=320&height=66" width="340" height="86" allownetworking="all"></p>    <div id="aplayer-OtPwTdBR" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker" data-id="002j785c33YQHT" data-server="tencent" data-type="song" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="true" data-listmaxheight="340px" data-preload="auto" data-theme="#ad7a86"></div><h2 id="为什么要搭建自己的个人博客"><a href="#为什么要搭建自己的个人博客" class="headerlink" title="为什么要搭建自己的个人博客?"></a><strong>为什么要搭建自己的个人博客?</strong></h2><blockquote><p>1、功利一点，为了好找工作！</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>2、从不喜欢做笔记的我，希望也开始用博客作为自己的学习记录</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>3、坚持写博客。有句话叫贵在坚持，去年也搭建过自己的个人博客，但是由于自己后来不小心把数据库给删了（我真是猪），然后就没有在写博客了。</p></blockquote><h5 id="最后，先来走一遍程序，来几个“Hello-World！”，哈哈哈。"><a href="#最后，先来走一遍程序，来几个“Hello-World！”，哈哈哈。" class="headerlink" title="最后，先来走一遍程序，来几个“Hello World！”，哈哈哈。"></a>最后，先来走一遍程序，来几个“Hello World！”，哈哈哈。</h5><pre class="line-numbers language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">HelloWorld</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Hello ,我的博客！"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><hr><pre class="line-numbers language-c++"><code class="language-c++">#include<iostream>using namespace std;int main(){    cout<<"Hello ,我的个人博客"<< endl;    return 0;}<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>    <div id="aplayer-BOaOYiOu" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker" data-id="001Mf4Ic1aNYYK" data-server="tencent" data-type="album" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="true" data-listmaxheight="180px" data-preload="auto" data-theme="#ad7a86" data-order="random"></div><hr><pre class="line-numbers language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Hello ,我的个人博客！"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>    <div id="aplayer-jXIqtPyB" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker" data-id="001Mf4Ic1aNYYK" data-server="tencent" data-type="album" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="true" data-listmaxheight="180px" data-preload="auto" data-theme="#ad7a86" data-order="random"></div>]]></content>
      
      
